{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/acme/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e31a679c-9d31-5c73-b0cc-5cff5443ca56","html":"<p>最近尝试用<code class=\"language-text\">Let&#39;s Encrypt</code>来添加通配符证书，发现之前的工具certbot在使用上有许多不方便之处。\n比如证书的注册时，<code class=\"language-text\">Let&#39;s Encrypt</code>会要求你配置dns解析来验证，这一点会影响证书的自动化更新，\n并且在安装时经常需要处理依赖的问题。最终转向新工具acme.sh，安装简单，使用方便。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-label=\"安装 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">curl https://get.acme.sh | sh</code></p>\n<p>提示安装成功后执行 <code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.bashrc</code>，就可以在命令行使用acme了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"申请证书\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E8%AF%81%E4%B9%A6\" aria-label=\"申请证书 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>申请证书</h2>\n<p>申请证书，可以直接执行<code class=\"language-text\">acme.sh  --issue  -d example.com -d *.example.com</code>\n注意这里我们同时申请了根域名和通配符域名。另外我在上面提到acme的好处之一，可以自动化dns验证：\n以阿里云为例，首先需要去阿里云dns控制面板获取api所需要的<code class=\"language-text\">App_Key</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">App_Secret</code>，</p>\n<!--more-->\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 替换成从阿里云dns后台获取的密钥</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">Ali_Key</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">Ali_Secret</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 换成自己的域名</span>\nacme.sh --issue --dns dns_ali -d example.com -d *.example.com</code></pre></div>\n<p>acme会通过线程等待120秒，申请大概需要2分多钟，成功后证书会存到<code class=\"language-text\">~/.acme.sh/example.com</code>目录。</p>\n<h2 id=\"启用证书\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%81%E4%B9%A6\" aria-label=\"启用证书 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>启用证书</h2>\n<p>这里有一点需要注意，默认生成的证书都放在安装目录下: <code class=\"language-text\">~/.acme.sh/</code>, 建议不要直接使用这个目录,\n这些文件大多是acme内部使用, 而且目录结构也可能会变化。</p>\n<p>正确的方式是使用 <code class=\"language-text\">--installcert</code> 指定目标位置, 然后证书文件会被复制到相应的位置：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">acme.sh --installcert <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --cert-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --key-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>.key<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --ca-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/ca.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --fullchain-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/fullchain.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --reloadcmd <span class=\"token string\">\"sudo service nginx force-reload\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>acme做了记忆化，会将上面的操作写入到cron任务中，但是sudo操作需要手动输入密码会比较麻烦，因此我们可以修改一下sudoer文件，让<code class=\"language-text\">sudo service nginx force-reload</code>不需要输入密码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> emacs /etc/sudoers</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后添加一行内容</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">test<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>登录名<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">ALL</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ALL<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> NOPASSWD: /usr/sbin/service nginx force-reload</code></pre></div>\n<p>这样，我们只需要在nginx中配置好证书的地址，就可以完成证书的全自动更新了</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">server <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    server_name example.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    listen <span class=\"token number\">443</span> ssl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># ssl on;</span>\n    ssl_certificate   /etc/nginx/cert.d/example.com/fullchain.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    ssl_certificate_key  /etc/nginx/cert.d/example.com/example.com.key<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"更新\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" aria-label=\"更新 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更新</h2>\n<p>acme在安装的时候往crontab增加了一行每天执行的命令，证书会在过期后自动更新, 你无需任何操作。</p>\n<h2 id=\"完整的脚本\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC\" aria-label=\"完整的脚本 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>完整的脚本</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 替换成从阿里云dns后台获取的密钥</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">Ali_Key</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">Ali_Secret</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">domain</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"your-domain.com\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> -p /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>\nacme.sh -d <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>\"</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"*.<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --issue --dns dns_ali <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --installcert <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --cert-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --key-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>.key<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --ca-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/ca.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --fullchain-file /etc/nginx/cert.d/<span class=\"token variable\">$domain</span>/fullchain.cer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --reloadcmd <span class=\"token string\">\"sudo service nginx force-reload\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 修改sudoer文件</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/acme/","tagSlugs":["/tag/web开发/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-11-29T22:40:32.169Z","description":"最近尝试用`Let's Encrypt`来添加通配符证书，发现之前的工具certbot在使用上有许多不方便之处。 比如证书的注册时，`Let's Encrypt`会要求你配置dns解析来验证，这一点会影响证书的自动化更新，并且在安装时经常需要处理依赖的问题。最终转向新工具acme.sh，安装简单，使用方便。","tags":["Web开发"],"title":"可持续更新的通配符证书申请","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/acme/"}}}